description: Papilly AB engages in the development and production of research based digital programs that aids consumer to lower the risk of mental illness. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2014-10-02. Its offering is aimed at reduction of stress-related lifestyle diseases. The firm offers an online platform, Stressklubben, which users are provided with help, knowledge, support and guidance to change their behavior and reduce stress. The company also provides possibilities of design, development and personalization of lifestyle change plans, help of experts in research, psychology, behaviorism and stress therapy, as well as gaming-related additional features. The firm's platform is also designed to support healthcare professionals specialized in stress, heart diseases, anxiety and relationship problems in the treatment process.
